      <h2 class="mt-3 font-serif text-3xl font-black text-[#24170f]">Newsletter + lifecycle + transactional</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-[17px] leading-8 text-[#4a2d17]">Capture layer (Privy or Justuno) feeds ESP welcome branches. ESP owns cart, post-purchase, replenishment, winback. Transactional shipping may stay Shopify or AfterShip — marketing suppresses when delivery delay tickets open. SMS for drop urgency pairs Postscript or Omnisend SMS with strict frequency caps; never duplicate email cart touch within two hours on SMS unless holdout testing.</p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-[17px] leading-8 text-[#4a2d17]">Sequenzy ranks first on this page when strategy speed and pay-per-email economics fit lean fashion stores teams — not because every merchant should avoid Klaviyo. Choose Klaviyo when predictive depth and SMS unity are daily tools; Omnisend when speed beats canvas complexity; Yotpo when reviews and loyalty already anchor retention model.</p>
